
Installing on linux (Ubuntu 20.04, debian bullseye, bookworm)
============================================================
== not use python virtual environment

== install (with apt-get,  aptitude)
mpv
libmpv-dev
git
python3-pip
libfreetype-dev
qtdeclarative5-dev
qml-module-qtquick-layouts
                  -dialogs
		  -controls
		  -controls2
qml-module-qt-labs-settings
qml-module-qt-labs-folderlistmodel
texlive
texlive-latex-extra

== (create and) start venv
==        python3 -m venv ~/Roeien/Meten/venv
. ~/Roeien/Meten/venv/bin/activate
== using pip install:
matplotlib==3.1.3
numpy scipy pyqt5 pyyaml openpyxl mplcursors pyperclip mpv pylatex

== the versions should be fairly recent, otherwise there are warnings or errors.
- Basic testing
    - Command:  pdflatex tstlatex.tex
       - yields a pdf file
    - Command:  python tstqtquick.py
       - yields a yellow window
    - Command:  python tstmatplotlib.py
       - a simple plot

